## Third-Party Services

This software integrates with third-party services that have their own terms:

### Telegram Bot API
- Terms: https://core.telegram.org/bots/faq#what-messages-will-my-bot-get
- Privacy: Messages sent through this bot are subject to Telegram's privacy policy

### Google Gemini API
- Terms: https://ai.google.dev/terms
- Privacy: Images processed by Gemini are subject to Google's AI service terms

### GitHub Actions
- Terms: https://docs.github.com/en/site-policy/github-terms/github-terms-of-service
- Usage: Free tier limits apply, see GitHub pricing for details

### Company Career Pages
- This software only accesses publicly available job listings
- Users are responsible for compliance with individual company terms of service
- No circumvention of access controls or rate limiting

